WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.660
Our model is a very simple one.

00:00:02.660 --> 00:00:07.440
It's a linear spline model and the only inputs are

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:10.480
time of the day, day of the week, and time of the year.

00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:15.400
Every five minutes we have a process in web methods

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:18.799
that reads data from the swimming pool gates

00:00:18.799 --> 00:00:21.360
and stores them in our data link.

00:00:21.360 --> 00:00:24.120
We then use the pins package.

00:00:24.120 --> 00:00:29.600
We get pinned linear models from our studio connect

00:00:29.799 --> 00:00:33.880
and we then predict the duration.

00:00:33.880 --> 00:00:38.560
Then we pin that results table in our studio connect

00:00:38.560 --> 00:00:42.520
and that's what our Shiny app accesses.

